title: [Empath Guild, Stone Gazebo]
description: Tidy beds of spotted mushrooms encircle a stone gazebo in riotous color.  A few stalagmites rise up in the background, the stone formations carved with fanciful, swirling patterns.  Thick, woven crimson curtains hang across the archways that line the cavern's walls.
paths: Obvious exits: north, northeast, east, west, northwest
